metadata.description: Slophy NFTs is a collection of 5000 utility NFTs that allows you special access to the Slophy App. Slophy is the first D2E (disconnect to Earn) platform that rewards you for taking a break from your smartphone. Slophy is open for all, but owning Slophy NFT allows you to see a hidden section on the app and the ability to gain rewards faster.
